The C/C++ tools in this directory link against libsidplayfp (GPL v2)
and/or wrap GoatTracker code (GPL v2). They are therefore distributed
under the GNU General Public License version 2.

See libsidplayfp/COPYING for the full GPL v2 text.

  siddump.cpp      — SID register dumper (links libsidplayfp)
  sidrender.cpp    — SID audio renderer (links libsidplayfp)
  test_libsid.cpp  — libsidplayfp test harness
  gt2asm.c         — GoatTracker assembler wrapper
  build.sh         — build script

The Python pipeline code in src/ is MIT licensed (see ../LICENSE).
